{
  "stem": "2460.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Absolutely-- even if it-- the camp was there, but the place was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know why they built a camp over there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We arrived there late at night, and we were walking from the train station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It's-- I don't know exactly the distance, but it's about a half an hour by walking to the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We arrived to the camp, to Mauthausen, and it was a different look to this camp than I used to the other camps.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This camp had tall, stone walls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And only above the stone was some barbed wire electric wires.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We walked into this big camp and taken right away to the showers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And in the showers, I saw the most terrible, the most horrifying thing that a human being can experience.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The kapos from Mauthausen camp [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] were ordered to kill the kapos from our camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now, in our working camp, the kapos were fairly human.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "One of them was a very nice Czechoslovakian boy who even helped me when I got big pants and a big shirt.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I always went to him and I told him, I am short and I'm small.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I can't walk in those heavy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So he always tried to exchange me in the-- for a smaller-- for a smaller shirt and smaller [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And this-- they were beating to death in the showers with like, baseball bats.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Not baseball bats, but with sticks, beating them to death.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we had about 12 or 13 kapos in our camp. 14, I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they were laying on the cement floor in the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
